<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你想不想听听
我之前在<delay8 />杂志上看到的占卜信息？！<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />超～级危险的哦～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="TakenAback" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />危险？<20_2 arg="4" /><delay40 />
怎么危险了？！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />上面说呀，<delay8 />
“你想要的东西，全都能拿到手”！<delay40 /><anim id="Thinking" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />超～级危险的对吧？！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />上面说呀，<delay8 />
“踏出家门就会好运连连！”<delay40 /><anim id="Thinking" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />超～级危险的对吧～？！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><20_2 arg="4" />不不不，<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你说的那些，<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不全都是<anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />好事吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然后啊，<20_2 arg="3" /><delay20 /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就出门去购物，<delay8 />
正好碰上<tag a="110" b="17" />的折扣活动，<delay8 />
买到了一件可爱的连衣裙！
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇，真的是太危险啦～！！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="TakenAback" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">是的呀～<20_2 arg="3" /><delay40 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然后啊，我就去<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="12" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的家里
一起玩<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />结果<delay8 />竟然收到了一件
上个月手头太紧，没买到的新衣服！<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的危险过头啦～！！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="TakenAback" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等等！<20_2 arg="4" /><delay20 />
这哪里危险啦？！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />倒不如说很幸运才对吧？<anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">所以呢，<20_2 arg="3" /><delay20 />我就穿着它出门去呀，<delay8 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />结果偶然遇到了<tag a="110" b="11" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，
被夸很好看哦～！
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />占卜的力量真的是<delay8 />太危险啦～！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="SadSpiral" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><20_3 arg="4" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你是在戏弄我吗？！<anim id="WrySmile" target="player" targetSpec="" /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是呢<20_2 arg="3" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><delay20 />穿着那件衣服出门之后，
突然又下起雨来了，<delay8 /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
整个人都被淋湿啦～！
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />太相信占卜的话<delay8 />也很危险的呀～<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="TakenAback" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><20_2 arg="4" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已经搞不清<delay8 />对你来说，<delay8 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="player" targetSpec="" />什么东西算是危险了！</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦～？！<delay40 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay20 />
你都不看动画的吗？<delay40 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />人生会少掉很多乐趣哦～！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />动画的剧情<20_2 arg="4" />进展太快了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />相比之下<delay8 />我还是更喜欢看漫画，
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />因为可以照着自己的步调来读啊！</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那不如<20_2 arg="3" />这样吧，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我把这一季我主推动画的原作漫画借给你，
你也<delay8 />读读看吧～！
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />来，<delay20 />就是这本“天空与森林之歌”哦！<delay8 /><anim id="Greeting" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />噢、<20_2 arg="4" /><delay8 />噢，<delay20 />
谢啦！<delay40 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这部漫画<delay8 />有意思吗？</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />噢，<20_2 arg="4" /><delay20 />如果是漫画的话我也看得下去！<delay40 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这部漫画<delay8 />有意思吗？</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 04 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这是一本<20_2 arg="3" />很老的作品啦，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过最近重回大众视野，<delay8 />
所以动画化了哦！
<20_2 arg="6" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，你应该也知道<20_3 arg="3" /><delay20 /><anim id="Eh" target="player" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="8" />
什么是<delay8 /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />“空森”对吧？</message>
	<message label="106_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">校园风还是好呀</message>
	<message label="106_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">很感动对吧～</message>
	<message label="106_c" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我不知道啊……</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我懂的～！<20_2 arg="7" /><delay40 />
而且还是<delay8 />寄宿制学校<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />妄想得根本<anim id="Shocked" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />停不下来啦～！</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对啊对啊～！<20_2 arg="7" /><delay40 /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看到主角和英雄那种
又伤感又凄美的悲恋，<delay8 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />整个人都会<anim id="Shocked" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />潸然泪下对吧～！</message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不是吧～？！<delay frames="60" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那这样的话，
我也可以顺便向<anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" /><delay8 />
推荐一下哦？</message>
	<message label="110" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">总之呢，<20_2 arg="2" /><delay20 />
既然<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />这么大力推荐，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这部作品应该相当有趣吧？</message>
	<message label="111" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />超～级有趣的！<delay40 />
你读完之后<delay8 />要记得再借给
<tag a="110" b="4" />哦！
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />顺便说一下这套书<delay8 />总共有71本，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之后我再把剩下的部分<delay8 />
搬到<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />家里去吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="112" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />71<tag a="110" b="0" />？！<delay20 />
竟然有那么多本吗<anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><20_3 arg="8" />好，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<20_3 arg="4" /><delay40 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Grin" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />我们彼此都拿出干劲来，<delay8 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="player" targetSpec="" />尽力把它给读完吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="113" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">虽然<20_2 arg="2" />我不是很懂，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="8" />不过既然<tag a="110" b="3" />也听说过，<delay8 />
<20_2 arg="7" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />就表示这部漫画应该挺热门的吧。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="114" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对啊～！<delay40 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还剩下70本呢，<delay8 />
我晚点再拿过去哦～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="115" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />71<tag a="110" b="0" />？！<delay40 />
竟然有那么多本吗<tag a="110" b="0" />！<pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好，<delay20 />男子汉决不食言！<delay40 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等下次休假的时候，<delay8 />
<anim id="Grin" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />我就静下心来看个够吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="116" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />读了漫画之后<delay8 />
你也就跟得上动画的剧情了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以不要忘记去看动画哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="117" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然感觉好像
完全中了你的圈套<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过我就奉陪到底吧！<anim id="Grin" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />你呀，<delay8 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的是太危险啦～！<anim id="SadSpiral" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呃啊～！<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="4" /><delay40 />
这次这个“危险”，<delay8 />
又是什么意思啊！
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你口中的“危险”，
能够表达的意思太多了，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />我每次都搞不清楚啊！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是这种感觉
才比较危险呀～！<anim id="Worried" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />你应该更<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对啦，<delay20 />应该想想办法，
