<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都在想些什么！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算<20_2 arg="4" /><delay8 />你这么说<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想到啦～！！<20_2 arg="3" /><delay40 /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你可以试着先从<delay8 />
学习我的说话方式开始嘛！
一开始可以只学一点点，<delay8 />怎么样？<anim id="TakenAback" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="206" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />谁<20_2 arg="4" /><delay8 />学得来啊！<anim id="Shocked" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />你挂在嘴边的口头禅<tag a="110" b="0" />
就是那句“<tag a="110" b="5" />”，<delay20 />
我应该也能用得上<tag a="110" b="0" />吧？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="207" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喔，<20_2 arg="3" /><delay8 />感觉还挺不错的嘛！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />通过学习我的口头禅，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />就能更理解少女的思维哦！</message>
	<message label="208" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />“<tag a="110" b="5" />”<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
“<tag a="110" b="5" />”<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
感觉好像<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还不错啊。<anim id="Clapping" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />不过，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这样做真的就能理解<delay8 />
